Author: Luke Sherwood
Title: 🏆 OPENBRIX - 4% OF MINT BOUNTY CAMPAIGN 🏆
Body: Whitepaper     Website     Lightpaper  »»--------------------------------¤--------------------------------««     Bitcointalk     Telegram     Twitter     Medium       Facebook     LinkedIn     Youtube     Reddit      »»-----------¤-----------««  Whitelist  ¤   Visionary simple idea. Globally renowned, high profile team. $100 bn market to disrupt.  OpenBrix will be the first blockchain powered decentralised property portal in Europe, Middle East, Africa (EMEA) and Asia, that will be fully open and inclusive to everyone. OpenBrix™ will be a decentralised network that connects all key players in the property letting and sales market on a single network. By creating a decentralised network there will be no single owner who controls the money, data or rules of the network. Everything will be community-run and done for the benefit of the community. It will be the true democratisation of the property rental and sales market.  Token value of 1 BRIX: 0.001ETH Total token genesis: 500,000,000 Total allocated for the bounties will be 4% of the mint total. This is the equivalent to over 20,000 ETH at the time of print.  A token can be used as a method to transact on the network, or as a method to make payments for products and services between the property owners and customers.  Initial Token Offering starts at 08:00 UTC on 8 July 2018.  Strategic sale now live! Join the whitelist now - the race is on!    All Campaigns Now Closed
